						</div>

						<div class="tab-panel" data-tab-panel="experience">
							<article class="card span-2">
								<h2>Software Engineer Intern — BC Liquor Distribution Branch</h2>
								<p class="muted">Jan 2025 – Aug 2025 · Vancouver, BC</p>
								<ul>
									<li>
										Upgraded 3 enterprise apps from Java 8/Spring Boot 2 to Java 17/Spring Boot 3
