									</li>
									<li>
										Resolved production defects and improved CI/CD deployment cycles by 40%.
									</li>
								</ul>
							</article>

							<article class="card span-2">
								<h2>Teaching Assistant — CPSC 110</h2>
								<p class="muted">Sep 2024 – Jan 2025 · UBC Vancouver, BC</p>
								<ul>
									<li>
										Led lab sessions and office hours for 1500+ students, translating CS concepts
										into solutions.
									</li>
									<li>
										Conducted 100+ weekly code reviews, emphasizing TDD and documentation
										practices.
									</li>
								</ul>
							</article>

							<article class="card span-2">
								<h2>Software Engineer Intern — Cynomatic Cyber Solutions</h2>
								<p class="muted">May 2024 – Aug 2024 · Calgary, AB</p>
								<ul>
									<li>
										Built an enterprise GenAI agent using LangChain and ChromaDB for 100+ internal
										documents.
									</li>
									<li>
										Engineered a React interface that increased site traffic and inbound lead
										generation by 20%.
									</li>
									<li>
										Automated marketing workflows in Python, increasing customer inquiries by 30%.
									</li>
								</ul>
							</article>
						</div>

						<div class="tab-panel" data-tab-panel="projects">
							<article class="card span-2">
								<h2>MLB Scoreboard Chrome Extension</h2>
								<p class="muted">May 2024 – Present · HTML, CSS, JS, Express, Node.js</p>
								<ul>
									<li>350+ daily active users and 1.2k+ total installs.</li>
									<li>
										AI recap endpoint using AWS Bedrock with caching, reducing response times by 40%.
									</li>
									<li>
										Express REST API with PostgreSQL (Supabase) for real-time updates.
									</li>
								</ul>
								<div class="project-media">
									<div class="project-image">Project preview</div>
									<a class="button" href="#" aria-disabled="true">View Demo</a>
								</div>
							</article>

							<article class="card span-2">
								<h2>Jarvis</h2>
								<p class="muted">Jan 2026 · LangGraph, OpenCV, Whisper, PyQt5</p>
								<ul>
									<li>Multimodal AI agent with real-time vision, OCR, and voice.</li>
									<li>Async Python backend with WebSockets for low-latency interactions.</li>
									<li>60 FPS HUD rendering with PyQt5 and OpenCV.</li>
								</ul>
								<div class="project-media">
									<div class="project-image">Project preview</div>
									<a class="button" href="#" aria-disabled="true">View Demo</a>
								</div>
							</article>

							<article class="card span-2">
								<h2>Emotion Playlist Generator</h2>
								<p class="muted">Jul 2025 – Aug 2025 · AWS Lambda, Rekognition</p>
								<ul>
									<li>Mood-based Spotify playlist generation.</li>
									<li>Emotion recognition pipeline with AWS Rekognition and Lambda.</li>
									<li>API Gateway integration for frontend communication.</li>
								</ul>
								<div class="project-media">
									<div class="project-image">Project preview</div>
									<a class="button" href="#" aria-disabled="true">View Demo</a>
								</div>
							</article>
						</div>

						<div class="tab-panel" data-tab-panel="resume">
							<article class="card span-2 resume-panel">
								<h2>Resume</h2>
								<p class="muted">Opening resume in a new tab…</p>
								<div class="resume-actions">
									<a class="button primary" href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Open Resume</a>
									<a class="button" href="/resume.pdf" download>Download Resume</a>
								</div>
							</article>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>

		<script>
			const output = document.getElementById('terminal-output');
			const form = document.getElementById('terminal-form');
			const input = document.getElementById('terminal-cmd');
			const shortcuts = document.querySelectorAll('[data-cmd]');
			const commands = {
				'cd ./about': 'about',
				'cd ./experience': 'experience',
				'cd ./projects': 'projects',
				'cd ./contact': 'contact',
				'open resume.pdf': 'resume'
			};

			const tabs = document.querySelectorAll('[data-tab]');
			const panels = document.querySelectorAll('[data-tab-panel]');
			let resumeOpened = false;

			const setActiveTab = (tabKey) => {
				tabs.forEach((tab) => {
					tab.classList.toggle('active', tab.dataset.tab === tabKey);
				});
				panels.forEach((panel) => {
					panel.classList.toggle('active', panel.dataset.tabPanel === tabKey);
				});
				if (tabKey === 'resume' && !resumeOpened) {
					window.open('/resume.pdf', '_blank');
					resumeOpened = true;
				}
			};

			const writeLine = (text, cls = '') => {
				const line = document.createElement('p');
				if (cls) line.classList.add(cls);
				line.textContent = text;
				output.appendChild(line);
				output.scrollTop = output.scrollHeight;
			};

			const runCommand = (cmd) => {
				const trimmed = cmd.trim();
				if (!trimmed) return;
				writeLine(`naman@portfolio:~$ ${trimmed}`);
				if (commands[trimmed]) {
					setActiveTab(commands[trimmed]);
					writeLine(`Switched to ${commands[trimmed]} tab`);
				} else if (trimmed === 'help') {
					writeLine('Available commands: cd ./about, cd ./experience, cd ./projects, cd ./contact, open resume.pdf');
				} else {
					writeLine('Command not found. Type help for options.', 'muted');
				}
			};

			tabs.forEach((tab) =>
				tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
					const tabKey = tab.dataset.tab || 'about';
					setActiveTab(tabKey);
					const targetId = tab.dataset.target;
					if (targetId) {
						const target = document.getElementById(targetId);
						if (target) {
							target.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
						}
					}
				})
			);

			form.addEventListener('submit', (event) => {
				event.preventDefault();
				runCommand(input.value);
				input.value = '';
			});

			shortcuts.forEach((btn) =>
				btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
					runCommand(btn.dataset.cmd || '');
				})
			);

			setActiveTab('about');
		</script>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:root {
		color-scheme: light;
		--bg: #f7f7fb;
		--surface: #ffffff;
		--surface-alt: #f0f2f7;
		--text: #141824;
		--muted: #586174;
		--accent: #2b6bf3;
		--accent-soft: rgba(43, 107, 243, 0.12);
		--border: rgba(20, 24, 36, 0.08);
		--shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
		--radius-lg: 24px;
		--radius-md: 16px;
		--radius-sm: 12px;
	}

	* {
		box-sizing: border-box;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}

	body {
		font-family: "SF Pro Display", "SF Pro Text", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Inter",
			"Segoe UI", sans-serif;
		background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #eef2ff 0%, #f7f7fb 55%, #ffffff 100%);
		color: var(--text);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	a {
		color: var(--accent);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.page {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 48px 24px 80px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 48px;
	}

	.hero {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 32px;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.hero__copy h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 4vw, 3.6rem);
		margin-bottom: 12px;
	}

	.eyebrow {
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.2em;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--muted);
		margin-bottom: 16px;
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--muted);
		max-width: 520px;
	}

	.hero__cta {
		display: flex;
		gap: 12px;
		margin: 24px 0 16px;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.hero__links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 12px;
		align-items: center;
		color: var(--muted);
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.button {
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		background: var(--surface);
		color: var(--text);
		padding: 10px 18px;
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-weight: 600;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
	}

	.button.primary {
		background: var(--accent);
		color: #fff;
		border-color: transparent;
	}

	.hero__panel {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 20px;
	}

	.terminal {
		background: var(--surface);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow);
	}

	.terminal__title {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 8px;
		padding: 12px 16px;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--muted);
	}

	.dot {
		width: 10px;
		height: 10px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.dot.red {
		background: #ff5f56;
	}

	.dot.yellow {
		background: #ffbd2e;
	}

	.dot.green {
		background: #27c93f;
	}

	.terminal__body {
		padding: 16px;
		max-height: 220px;
		overflow-y: auto;
		font-family: "SF Mono", "Fira Code", monospace;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}

	.prompt {
		color: #3d7eff;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-right: 6px;
	}

	.terminal__input {
		display: flex;
		gap: 8px;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 12px 16px 16px;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.terminal__input input {
		flex: 1;
		border: none;
		background: transparent;
		font-family: "SF Mono", "Fira Code", monospace;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--text);
		outline: none;
	}

	.terminal__shortcuts {
		display: flex;
		gap: 8px;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		padding: 0 16px 16px;
	}

	.terminal__shortcuts button {
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		background: var(--surface-alt);
		border-radius: 999px;
		padding: 6px 12px;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		cursor: pointer;
	}


	.ide {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(200px, 230px) 1fr;
		gap: 0;
		background: var(--surface);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow);
	}

	.ide__sidebar {
		background: #f3f4f8;
		padding: 20px;
		border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.ide__title {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		color: var(--muted);
		margin-bottom: 16px;
	}

	.ide__sidebar ul {
		list-style: none;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--text);
	}

	.folder {
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 8px;
	}

	.file {
		color: var(--muted);
		margin-bottom: 6px;
	}

	.file button {
		border: none;
		background: none;
		font: inherit;
		color: inherit;
		padding: 0;
		cursor: pointer;
		text-align: left;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.file button.active {
		color: var(--text);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.indent {
		padding-left: 16px;
	}

	.ide__main {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}

	.ide__tabs {
		display: flex;
		gap: 8px;
		padding: 12px 16px;
		background: var(--surface-alt);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.tab {
		padding: 6px 12px;
		border-radius: 10px;
		background: transparent;
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		border: none;
		cursor: pointer;
	}

	.tab.active {
		background: #fff;
		color: var(--text);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
	}

	.grid {
		padding: 24px;
		background: #fff;
	}

	.tab-panel {
		display: none;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 20px;
	}

	.tab-panel.active {
		display: grid;
	}

	.card {
		background: var(--surface);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
		padding: 20px;
		box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
	}

	.card h2 {
		margin-bottom: 12px;
	}

	.card h3 {
		margin: 10px 0 4px;
	}

	.span-2 {
		grid-column: span 2;
	}

	.muted {
		color: var(--muted);
	}

	.pill-group {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 8px;
		margin-top: 12px;
	}

	.pill-group span {
		background: var(--accent-soft);
		color: var(--accent);
		border-radius: 999px;
		padding: 6px 12px;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.timeline {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 16px;
	}

	.timeline ul,
	.projects ul {
		padding-left: 18px;
		color: var(--muted);
	}

	.projects {
		display: grid;
		gap: 16px;
	}

	.resume-panel {
		display: grid;
		gap: 16px;
	}

	.resume-actions {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 12px;
	}

	.project-media {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 12px;
		margin-top: 16px;
	}

	.project-image {
		height: 160px;
		border-radius: 14px;
		border: 1px dashed var(--border);
		background: var(--surface-alt);
		display: grid;
		place-items: center;
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}

	.contact-form {
		display: grid;
		gap: 12px;
	}

